<% content_for :title, "Terms of Service — Allimgtools" %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
  <p class="text-base-content/40 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: <%= Date.new(2026, 5, 3).strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

  <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none space-y-8">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">1. About This Service</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        Allimgtools provides online image processing tools — including compression, resizing, conversion, cropping, rotation, and EXIF metadata removal.
        You can use these tools without creating an account.
        An account (via Google Sign-In) is required only to subscribe to the Pro plan.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">2. Your Files</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        Files you upload are processed on our servers and automatically deleted within 3 hours.
        We do not store, analyze, share, or use your images for any purpose beyond the immediate processing task you requested.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">3. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed mb-2">You agree not to use Allimgtools to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-base-content/70">
        <li>Upload illegal, harmful, or copyrighted content you do not have rights to</li>
        <li>Attempt to disrupt, overload, or exploit the service</li>
        <li>Use automated tools to abuse the service in a way that impacts other users</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">4. Account</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        When you sign in with Google, we store your name, email address, and profile picture to identify your account.
        We do not receive or store your Google password.
        You can delete your account at any time from your <a href="/my-page" class="underline hover:text-base-content">My Page</a>.
        If you have an active Pro subscription, please cancel it before deleting your account.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">5. Pro Plan & Billing</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3 text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          The Pro plan is a monthly subscription billed at $5/month. Payments are processed securely by Paddle, our Merchant of Record.
          We do not store your payment card details.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-medium text-base-content">Cancellation:</span>
          You may cancel your subscription at any time from your <a href="/my-page" class="underline hover:text-base-content">My Page</a>.
          Upon cancellation, your Pro access remains active until the end of the current billing period. You will not be charged again after that.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-medium text-base-content">Refunds:</span>
          Refund requests are handled on a case-by-case basis. Please contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@allimgtools.com" class="underline hover:text-base-content">support@allimgtools.com</a> and we will do our best to help.
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-medium text-base-content">Price changes:</span>
          We reserve the right to change the subscription price. We will notify subscribers by email with at least 30 days' notice before any price change takes effect.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">6. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        Allimgtools is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind.
        We are not liable for any loss of data, damages, or issues arising from the use of this service.
        We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the service at any time without prior notice.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">7. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the service after changes are posted means you accept the updated terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">8. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        These terms are issued by <span class="font-medium text-base-content">Allimgtools</span>.
        If you have any questions, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:support@allimgtools.com" class="underline hover:text-base-content">support@allimgtools.com</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>
